Symbol.Script_3D:
!! TV.gsm
if gs_detlevel_3D_m = DLEV3D_OFF then end if gs_detlevel_3D_m = DLEV3D_SIMPLE then gs_resol = 3
IF gs_shadow=0 then SHADOW OFF
pen gs_cont_pen
r1=1.2 !horizontal radius of the screen r2=1 !vertical radius of the screen
c=zzyzx
RESOL gs_resol MATERIAL box_mat addz 0.01 rotx 90 mulz -1 extrude 21,0,0,b/2,1+2+4+16+32, 0, -0.01, 1, a/8, -0.01, 1, a/8, 0, 1, a*7/8, 0, 1, a*7/8, -0.01, 1, a, -0.01, 1, a, c-0.01, 1, a-0.01, c,1001, 0.01, c, 1, 0, c-0.01,1001, 0, -0.01, -1,
a/8+0.01, c/8, 1, a*7/8-0.01, c/8, 1, a*7/8,c/8+0.01,1001, a*7/8,c*7/8-0.01, 1, a*7/8-0.01,c*7/8,1001, a/8+0.01,c*7/8, 1, a/8,c*7/8-0.01,1001, a/8, c/8+0.01, 1, a/8+0.01,c/8,1001, a/8+0.01,c/8,-1 del 2
addy b/2 rotx -90 sweep 5,2,0,1/2,2+4+32, a/8,-c/8,0, a*7/8,-c/8,0, a*7/8,-c*7/8,0, a/8,-c*7/8,0, a/8,-c/8,-1, a/2,-c/2,0, a/2,-c/2,b/2 del 2
fi1=asn(a*3/8/r1) fi2=asn(c*3/8/r2)
MATERIAL scmat resol 96 add a/8,b/8,c/8 prism_ 7,c*6/8, 0,0,79, cos(fi1),-sin(fi1),815, a*6/8,0,1015, a*6/8,b/4,79, -cos(fi1),-sin(fi1),800, 0,b/4,1015, 0,0,-1 del 1 resol 36
MATERIAL spmat addz c/8 rotx 90 block a/8,c*6/8,0.001 addx a*7/8 block a/8,c*6/8,0.001 del 1 del 2
MATERIAL sgmat add a*7/16,0,c*3/64 rotx 90 block a/8,c/32,0.001 del 2
del 1
Symbol.Script_2D:
!! TV.gsm
pen gs_cont_pen
rect2 0,0,A,B/2 add2 A/8,B/2 poly2_ 5,1, 0,0,1, A*6/8,0,1, A*4.5/8,B/2,1, A*1.5/8,B/2,1, 0,0,-1 del 1
hotspot2 A/2,B hotspot2 A/2,B/2 hotspot2 0,B/2 hotspot2 A,B/2 hotspot2 A*5.5/8,B hotspot2 A*2.5/8,B
CALL "Resize_A_B_ZZYZX" Parameters ALL
fill gs_fill_type poly2_B 9, 1+2+4+64, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, 0,0,1, A,0,1, A,B/2,1, A*7/8,B/2,1, A*5.5/8,B,1, A*2.5/8,B,1, A/8,B/2,1, 0,B/2,1, 0,0,-1
Symbol.Script_1D: ! const values for parameter: gs_detlevel_3D_m DLEV3D_OFF = 0 DLEV3D_SIMPLE = 1 DLEV3D_DETAILED = 2 DLEV3D_DRAFT = 3
Symbol.Script_VL:
call "FM_types" parameters all
hideparameter all "A", "B", "ZZYZX"
VALUES "a" RANGE [0.1,) VALUES "b" RANGE [0.1,) VALUES "zzyzx" RANGE [0.1,) values{2} "gs_detlevel_3D_m" DLEV3D_DETAILED, `Детальный`, DLEV3D_SIMPLE, `Простой`, DLEV3D_OFF, `Откл.` VALUES "gs_resol" RANGE [3,)
if gs_cont_pen=0 then parameters gs_cont_pen=10 if gs_fill_pen=0 then parameters gs_fill_pen=91
IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = DLEV3D_SIMPLE THEN HIDEPARAMETER "gs_resol" IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = DLEV3D_OFF THEN HIDEPARAMETER "gs_resol", "gs_shadow"
